I never even noticed it was gone.

742
00:32:29,196 --> 00:32:31,496
还有谁有权进入这间办公室
Who else has access to the office?

743
00:32:31,498 --> 00:32:32,798
Dorsey上校
Captain Dorsey.

744
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:34,032
Dorsey在哪里
Where is Dorsey?

745
00:32:37,938 --> 00:32:40,072
这不是谈判
This is not a negotiation.

746
00:32:40,074 --> 00:32:42,407
我们没有选择 上尉
We don't have a choice, Lieutenant.

747
00:32:42,409 --> 00:32:44,309
我只是说 也许我们应该听他们的
All I'm saying is maybe we should listen to them.

748
00:32:44,311 --> 00:32:45,544
我们没做错什么事
We didn't do anything wrong.

749
00:32:45,546 --> 00:32:47,312
Lewis是因我们而死
Lewis is dead because of us!

750
00:32:47,314 --> 00:32:49,314
我们是奉命去凌辱他
We were ordered to haze him,

751
00:32:49,316 --> 00:32:51,917
就像现在我们也是在奉命行事
just like we were ordered to do this.

752
00:32:51,919 --> 00:32:54,086
我们没有杀Lewis 更没有杀Noah律师
We didn't kill Lewis any more than we killed JAG Noah.

753
00:32:54,088 --> 00:32:56,455
你认为外面的人会在乎这个吗
You think anyone outside of here cares about that?

754
00:32:56,457 --> 00:32:58,190
这里所代表的一切都处于危险中
Everything this place stands for is on the line.

755
00:32:58,192 --> 00:32:59,524
你明白吗
Do you understand?

756
00:32:59,526 --> 00:33:01,960
我们服从命令 就这样
We follow orders. Period.

757
00:33:01,962 --> 00:33:04,496
但是最初 正是服从命令才让我们
But following orders is what got us into this mess

758
00:33:04,498 --> 00:33:06,164
陷入这件事
in the first place.

759
00:33:09,470 --> 00:33:11,737
Rita
Rita!

760
00:33:13,273 --> 00:33:15,474
我很抱歉这么说 Dwayne 但我认为这证明了
I'm sorry to say this, Dwayne, but I think this proves

761
00:33:15,476 --> 00:33:17,009
我对学员的看法是对的
I was right about the cadets.

762
00:33:17,011 --> 00:33:18,844
事实上 我认为他们被陷害了
Actually, I think they're being set up.

763
00:33:18,846 --> 00:33:21,113
我认为不是学员们杀了Lewis或者Noah
I don't think any of the cadets killed Lewis or Noah.

764
00:33:21,115 --> 00:33:24,182
-证据呢 -你看到Dorsey上校了吗
- Based on what? - Have you seen Captain Dorsey?

765
00:33:24,184 --> 00:33:26,051
Dorsey 我们刚让他进去 怎么了
Dorsey, we just sent him inside. Why?

766
00:33:36,397 --> 00:33:38,597
原地候命
Stand down.

767
00:33:43,437 --> 00:33:46,371
你本该控制住局面的 学员
You were supposed to contain the situation, Cadet.

768
00:33:47,408 --> 00:33:49,107
现在我得来收拾摊子
Now I have to clean it up.

769
00:33:50,477 --> 00:33:51,810
跟我来
With me.

770
00:34:08,363 --> 00:34:11,998
我想说的是 情况可能不像看起来那样
All I'm saying is, the situation may not be as it appears.

771
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:13,166
我们认为Cabral少校
We think Commander Cabral's

772
00:34:13,168 --> 00:34:15,735
被你们刚放进去的人陷害了
being set up by the man you just let inside.

773
00:34:15,737 --> 00:34:17,537
Cabral扣留了两名你的人当人质
Cabral is holding two of your own people hostage.

774
00:34:17,539 --> 00:34:19,439
他只是在服从命令
He's just following orders.

775
00:34:19,441 --> 00:34:21,541
我也一样 我的工作是清除危险 Pride探员
And so am I. My job is clear, Agent Pride,

776
00:34:21,543 --> 00:34:23,810
就是要尽我所能去缓和局势
and that's to defuse the situation any way I can.

777
00:34:23,812 --> 00:34:25,812
-Dugan -失陪
- Dugan? - Excuse me.

778
00:34:25,814 --> 00:34:27,313
这说不通
This doesn't make any sense.

779
00:34:27,315 --> 00:34:28,681
如果你是对的 那些男孩是无罪的
If you're right, and the boys are innocent,

780
00:34:28,683 --> 00:34:31,284
为什么要这么做 为什么要扣留人质
why do this? Why take hostages?

781
00:34:31,286 --> 00:34:33,519
整个改造的前提是教会学员们
The whole premise of reform here is to teach cadets

782
00:34:33,521 --> 00:34:34,887
绝对服从命令
to obey orders without question,

783
00:34:34,889 --> 00:34:37,023
把军校放在第一位
to put the academy first.

784
00:34:37,025 --> 00:34:39,459
显然 Dorsey利用了这点
Obviously, Dorsey took advantage of that.

785
00:34:39,461 --> 00:34:42,395
等等 你是说Dorsey杀了Noah和Lewis 为什么
Wait, you're saying Dorsey killed Noah and, and Lewis? Why?

786
00:34:42,397 --> 00:34:44,631
-Pride -跟我说说情况
- Pride. - Talk to me.

787
00:34:44,633 --> 00:34:47,066
上将让我查阅了Dorsey的人事档案
The general got me access to Dorsey's personnel files.

788
00:34:47,068 --> 00:34:49,102
看样子 在上一位上将死后
Apparently, he applied to take over the academy

789
00:34:49,104 --> 00:34:51,904
他申请了接管学校 但是却由Walsh接管了
after the last general died, but Walsh got it instead.

790
00:34:51,906 --> 00:34:53,806
-这不是谋杀的动机 -是的
- That's not motivation for murder. - Well, no.

791
00:34:53,808 --> 00:34:55,942
但他被否决的主要原因却可能成为动机
But the main reason that he got passed over might be.

792
00:34:55,944 --> 00:34:57,377
Dorsey曾多次因滥用职权
See, Dorsey had been reprimanded several times

793
00:34:57,379 --> 00:34:58,678
而被谴责
for abuse of authority,

794
00:34:58,680 --> 00:35:00,880
包括下达凌辱学员的命令
including ordering the hazing of cadets.

795
00:35:00,882 --> 00:35:03,516
所以Lewis这事做得过火了
So things with Lewis went too far,

796
00:35:03,518 --> 00:35:06,252
不受他们失控了 Noah律师发现了
they got out of hand, JAG Noah figured it out...

797
00:35:06,254 --> 00:35:07,420
他不得不也杀了他
And he had to kill him, too.

798
00:35:07,422 --> 00:35:08,788
还是解释不了为什么Cabral
Still doesn't explain why Cabral

799
00:35:08,790 --> 00:35:10,290
封锁了学校
locked down the school.

800
00:35:10,292 --> 00:35:11,991
不 可以解释
No, it does.

801
00:35:11,993 --> 00:35:14,694
这能说通 如果他是奉了Dorsey的命令
It does, if he's following Dorsey's orders.

802
00:35:14,696 --> 00:35:18,331
而Dorsey想让Max看起来有罪...
And if Dorsey's trying to make Max look guilty...

803
00:35:19,801 --> 00:35:21,634
Gregorio在哪里
Where's Gregorio?

804
00:35:22,871 --> 00:35:24,570
我们只有一次机会
We only got one shot at this.

805
00:35:24,572 --> 00:35:28,174
收到 Pride 我只希望我们有足够的时间
Got it, Pride. I just hope we have enough time.

806
00:35:29,944 --> 00:35:31,678
嘿 如果你是无罪的
Hey. If you're innocent,

807
00:35:31,680 --> 00:35:34,480
如果Max是无罪的 我们可以证明
if Max is innocent, we can prove it,

808
00:35:34,482 --> 00:35:36,382
但不是这样
But not like this.

809
00:35:36,384 --> 00:35:38,785
除此之外 就连军队都会不遵守命令
Besides, even the military's not supposed to follow orders

810
00:35:38,787 --> 00:35:40,253
如果命令是不合法的
if they're illegal,

811
00:35:40,255 --> 00:35:42,722
或者犯法的 嘿 你也一样
or criminal... hey, and neither are you.

812
00:35:42,724 --> 00:35:44,457
如果你想做正确的事
Look, if you want to do what's right?

813
00:35:44,459 --> 00:35:45,892
你怎么回事
What is wrong with you?

814
00:35:45,894 --> 00:35:48,328
我们可以趁早停止这些
We can stop this before it's too late.

815
00:35:48,330 --> 00:35:50,330
你能阻止
You can stop this.

816
00:35:50,332 --> 00:35:52,732
但请你
But please,

817
00:35:52,734 --> 00:35:54,934
让我们走
let us go.

818
00:35:59,808 --> 00:36:02,175
你是军队的耻辱
You are an embarrassment to the uniform.

819
00:36:02,177 --> 00:36:03,943
这是你的烂摊子 少校
This is your mess, Commander.

820
00:36:03,945 --> 00:36:05,244
我是服从你的命令
I was following your orders.

821
00:36:05,246 --> 00:36:07,280
我的命令是保护学校
My orders were to protect the academy,

822
00:36:07,282 --> 00:36:08,815
不是把它置于险境
not to put it at risk,

823
00:36:08,817 --> 00:36:10,583
而那却是你所做的
which is exactly what you've done.

824
00:36:10,585 --> 00:36:11,972
你到底在想什么
What the hell were you thinking?

825
00:36:11,996 --> 00:36:13,220
你是开始这一切的人
You're the one that started this.

826
00:36:13,221 --> 00:36:15,588
是你让我凌辱Lewis 吓吓他
You're the one that told me to haze Lewis, scare him straight.

827
00:36:15,590 --> 00:36:17,423
但你做过头了 不是吗
But you went too far, didn't you?

828
00:36:17,425 --> 00:36:18,991
Lewis威胁说要把事情抖出来
Lewis threatened to expose it,

829
00:36:18,993 --> 00:36:20,927
但那就破坏了学校的制度
but that would've brought down the very institution

830
00:36:20,929 --> 00:36:22,095
你就要在监狱里
that's kept you from spending the rest

831
00:36:22,097 --> 00:36:23,763
度过你可怜的余生
of your sorry-ass life in prison.

832
00:36:23,765 --> 00:36:25,098
我没有杀Lewis
I didn't kill Lewis!

833
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:26,499
但我不得不
But I had to!

834
00:36:26,501 --> 00:36:28,000
为了保护学校
To protect the academy

835
00:36:28,002 --> 00:36:29,669
免受同样的混乱
from the same mess.

836
00:36:29,671 --> 00:36:31,671
那Noah律师呢
What about JAG Noah?

837
00:36:31,673 --> 00:36:33,773
也算你头上
Also on you.

838
00:36:33,775 --> 00:36:36,275
在他弄明白发生了什么之后
After he figured out what happened,

839
00:36:36,277 --> 00:36:37,977
找到了Lewis的尸体
tracked down Lewis's body,

840
00:36:37,979 --> 00:36:41,481
我必须做点什么 来保护我们免遭你的连累
I had to do something to protect us all from your screwups!

841
00:36:41,483 --> 00:36:43,349
忠诚高于一切
Loyalty above all else!

842
00:36:45,120 --> 00:36:47,019
记得吗
Remember that?

843
00:36:47,021 --> 00:36:49,021
那是这个地方所代表的意义
That's what this place stands for.

844
00:36:49,023 --> 00:36:51,624
但显然你没有做到
But that's something you obviously don't get.

845
00:36:51,626 --> 00:36:52,992
你是个失败者 Cabral
You're a failure, Cabral,

846
00:36:52,994 --> 00:36:55,294
对你自己 对学校 都是失败者
a failure to yourself, and this institution.

847
00:36:55,296 --> 00:36:57,897
你应该为你自己感到羞耻
You should be ashamed of yourself!

848
00:36:58,833 --> 00:37:01,300
我可以开火吗
Do I have permission to fire?

849
00:37:01,302 --> 00:37:02,869
你以为你控制了一切吗
You think you got the balls?

850
00:37:02,871 --> 00:37:05,705
来啊 开枪啊 朝我开枪
Go ahead, pull the trigger! Shoot me!

851
00:37:05,707 --> 00:37:08,007
不行 但我可以 挪开
No, but I do. Move.

852
00:37:11,379 --> 00:37:13,446
来啊
Do it!

853
00:37:21,723 --> 00:37:23,322
联邦探员 不许动
Federal agents! Don't move!

854
00:37:23,324 --> 00:37:25,358
举起手来
Put your hands up!

855
00:37:36,004 --> 00:37:37,470
警报解除 警报解除
All clear, all clear.

856
00:37:37,472 --> 00:37:39,105
漂亮的一枪 Gregorio
Nice shot, Gregorio.

857
00:37:39,107 --> 00:37:40,506
我知道你可以做到
I knew you could do it.

858
00:37:40,508 --> 00:37:41,741
等你下来了再见
See you when you get back down here.

859
00:37:41,743 --> 00:37:42,708
收到
Copy that.

860
00:37:42,710 --> 00:37:44,076
只是出于好奇
Just out of curiosity,

861
00:37:44,078 --> 00:37:45,244
你怎么知道那个计划可行
how'd you know that would work?

862
00:37:45,246 --> 00:37:46,712
那是Dorsey的计划吗
That that was Dorsey's plan?

863
00:37:46,714 --> 00:37:48,781
我不知道 我不清楚
I didn't, but I couldn't figure out

864
00:37:48,783 --> 00:37:50,383
他还会做什么
what else he was gonna do.

865
00:37:50,385 --> 00:37:53,486
穷途末路 知道我们要逮捕他
Backed in the corner, knew we were onto him,

866
00:37:53,488 --> 00:37:55,121
假设事态会升级
assumed things would escalate.

867
00:37:55,123 --> 00:37:57,723
所以 换句话说 这只是直觉吗
So, in other words, it was just a hunch?

868
00:37:57,725 --> 00:38:00,426
我更乐意说是"有依据的推测"
I prefer “educated guess.”

869
00:38:14,275 --> 00:38:18,144
还是不能完全了解他
Still can't quite figure him out.

870
00:38:18,146 --> 00:38:20,646
了解谁 Pride吗
Figure out who? Pride?

871
00:38:20,648 --> 00:38:22,281
-对 -他有什么好了解的
- Yeah. - What's there to figure out?

872
00:38:22,283 --> 00:38:23,483
他就是那种人啊
He's the man.

873
00:38:23,485 --> 00:38:25,284
我想她说的是他的私生活
I think she's talking about his personal life.

874
00:38:25,286 --> 00:38:26,652
哦
Oh.

875
00:38:26,654 --> 00:38:28,221
弹钢琴是他的私生活
Yeah, but playing piano is his personal life.

876
00:38:28,223 --> 00:38:29,922
不 还有比这个更私密的事情
Nah, there's got to be more to it than that.

877
00:38:29,924 --> 00:38:31,524
他这么优质的男人
He's such a good catch.

878
00:38:33,127 --> 00:38:35,628
他不应该被人勾搭吗 不是吗
I mean, he should be hooked up with someone, no?

879
00:38:37,765 --> 00:38:41,801
把话说清楚 现在聊的只是出于职业好奇
Talking professional curiosity here, let's just be clear.

880
00:38:41,803 --> 00:38:43,970
King并不急着
Look, King is not in a hurry to get together

881
00:38:43,972 --> 00:38:45,404
找个人在一起
with anyone anytime soon.

882
00:38:45,406 --> 00:38:47,840
他喜欢当King
He's just happy being King.

883
00:38:47,842 --> 00:38:49,775
没错 好吧 像我刚刚说的
It's true. Okay. Well, like I said,

884
00:38:49,777 --> 00:38:52,478
他是个优质男 只是不大符合常理罢了
he's a great catch, and it's just not natural.

885
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:54,881
你只是因为输掉了关于Rita的打赌而不爽
You're just cranky that you lost the bet about Rita.

886
00:38:54,883 --> 00:38:57,083
-对了 -没错 我都忘了
- Bingo. - Exactly! I forgot.

887
00:38:57,083 --> 00:38:57,483
我有不爽吗
I'm cranky? I'm cranky?

888
00:38:57,485 --> 00:39:00,253
-对 你有 -那她为什么来了
- Yeah, you cranky. - Then why is she here?

889
00:39:00,255 --> 00:39:01,787
啊哈
Huh?

890
00:39:08,463 --> 00:39:10,763
看来你还记得我的话
I see I made an impression on you.

891
00:39:10,765 --> 00:39:12,865
是吗 弹的怎么样
Oh, yeah? How's that?

892
00:39:12,867 --> 00:39:15,301
轻敲琴键 没那么紧绷了
Lighter touch on the keys, less tense.

893
00:39:15,303 --> 00:39:17,069
好吧 你非常有自信
All right, you're pretty confident.

894
00:39:17,071 --> 00:39:18,604
还好啦
Uh, not so much.

895
00:39:18,606 --> 00:39:21,274
在我差点酿成惨剧之后 就没那么自信了
Certainly not after I nearly caused a disaster.

896
00:39:21,276 --> 00:39:22,708
你太苛责你自己了
You're being too hard on yourself.

897
00:39:22,710 --> 00:39:24,677
还有什么新鲜的
Eh. What else is new?

898
00:39:24,679 --> 00:39:26,512
我早该知道
I should've known better.

899
00:39:26,514 --> 00:39:27,914
我应该记住的
I should've remembered.

900
00:39:27,916 --> 00:39:30,116
永远不要和你的直觉过不去
Never go up against one of your hunches.

901
00:39:30,118 --> 00:39:33,486
我不知道 我的方法也有跑偏的时候
Oh, I don't know, my way could've gone sideways, too.

902
00:39:33,488 --> 00:39:35,555
鉴于那些孩子在上军校前
Troubled history those kids had even before

903
00:39:35,557 --> 00:39:37,290
问题重重的历史 很难不想到
they get to the academy, hard not to think

904
00:39:37,292 --> 00:39:39,825
无风不起浪
that where there's smoke, there's fire.

905
00:39:39,827 --> 00:39:41,894
这就是Dorsey上校希望
Well, certainly what Captain Dorsey was hoping

906
00:39:41,896 --> 00:39:43,729
让大家相信的事情
to make everybody believe.

907
00:39:43,731 --> 00:39:45,831
地方检察署认为他不仅试图陷害Max
D.A. thinks he wasn't just trying to frame Max,

908
00:39:45,833 --> 00:39:48,634
还想让Walsh难看 这样他就能接管学校
but also make Walsh look bad so he could take over.

909
00:39:48,636 --> 00:39:51,404
可是却差点搞垮了学校
Almost brought down the academy instead.

910
00:39:51,406 --> 00:39:53,806
谢谢为他们的行为说了好话
Thanks for putting in a good word on their behalf.

911
00:39:53,808 --> 00:39:56,609
这是我最起码能做的事情了
Oh, it's the least I could do.

912
00:39:56,611 --> 00:40:00,947
毕竟 那些孩子值得拥有第二次机会
After all, those boys deserve a second chance.

913
00:40:00,949 --> 00:40:02,682
没错 我同意
Yeah, I agree with that.

914
00:40:04,852 --> 00:40:06,519
继续说
Yeah, go ahead.

915
00:40:06,521 --> 00:40:08,621
对了
By the way...

916
00:40:10,592 --> 00:40:12,158
记得这个吗
Remember this one?

917
00:40:12,160 --> 00:40:15,061
别 拜托 别弹那个
No-- don't. Please, don't go there.

918
00:40:15,063 --> 00:40:16,829
怎么 你害怕了
What, are you scared?

919
00:40:15,063 --> 00:40:16,829
